    <item>
      <title>信用风险持续存在，韩国经济保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/south-korea-s-economic-growth-holds-steady-as-credit-risks-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于出口保持势头，韩国上季度经济增长保持稳定，但挥之不去的信贷风险给议会选举前的前景蒙上了阴影，而议会选举对韩国总统尹锡烈的政策举措至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/south-korea-s-economic-growth-holds-steady-as-credit-risks-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉盈利未达预期，警告增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/tesla-earnings-miss-forecasts-warns-about-slower-growth-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 公布的第四季度收益未达到预期，并警告 2024 年销售增长“显着下降”。埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-24/tesla-earnings-miss-forecasts-warns-about-slower-growth-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>HPE 表示相信最近的黑客攻击是与俄罗斯有关的组织幕后黑手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/hpe-says-it-was-hacked-by-group-believed-to-be-midnight-blizzard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠普企业公司 (Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co.) 表示，一名可疑的民族国家行为者未经授权访问了其基于云的电子邮件系统，这将矛头指向了一个也涉嫌参与最近微软公司黑客攻击的组织。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/hpe-says-it-was-hacked-by-group-believed-to-be-midnight-blizzard</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:29:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ServiceNow 预计销售将强劲增长，但需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/servicenow-projects-stronger-than-expected-revenue-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ServiceNow Inc. 提供的本季度收入前景超出了华尔街的预期，同时对未来业务增长给出了保守的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/servicenow-projects-stronger-than-expected-revenue-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:11:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉表示，由于生产低成本汽车，其增长“明显放缓”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tesla-says-growth-rate-to-slow-in-2024-reports-earnings-miss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司 (Tesla Inc.) 警告称，由于该公司生产下一代汽车，即在奥斯汀工厂生产的低成本汽车，2024 年销量增长将放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/tesla-says-growth-rate-to-slow-in-2024-reports-earnings-miss</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:11:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IBM 预计 2024 年销售额和自由现金流将强劲；计划裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ibm-sees-strong-2024-free-cash-flow-plans-job-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际商业机器公司 (International Business Machines Corp.) 对 2024 年收入和现金流做出了积极的展望，这是对企业技术支出步伐的乐观信号，尽管该公司预计将减少就业岗位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/ibm-sees-strong-2024-free-cash-flow-plans-job-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:09:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官表示，新的 FTX 破产调查应该是有限且快速的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/new-ftx-bankruptcy-probe-should-be-limited-and-fast-judge-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官采取行动限制对饱受欺诈困扰的加密货币公司 FTX Trading 进行新的外部调查的成本和时间，并表示其破产案不应因另一项耗资数百万美元的调查而中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/new-ftx-bankruptcy-probe-should-be-limited-and-fast-judge-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:08:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alphabet 股价因人工智能炒作而创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/alphabet-flirts-with-record-high-as-ai-hype-propels-stock-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 股价周三飙升，并在盘中交易中短暂超越了该公司的历史最高收盘价，原因是对其人工智能能力的乐观情绪提振了该股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/alphabet-flirts-with-record-high-as-ai-hype-propels-stock-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:33:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
